## ğŸ”§ Features

- Add tasks with `POST /tasks`
- Mark tasks as completed with `PUT /tasks/{id}/complete`
- Validate blockchain integrity via `GET /tasks/validate`
- View the blockchain: `GET /tasks/chain`
- Crawl productivity articles from the web
- Save the chain to `blockchain.json` for persistence

